overview:
i95Dev comprises a team of strategists, architects, developers, designers and consultants who work together to develop custom solutions for client’s needs.

i95Dev has extensive experience across all sectors of B2B & B2C and created much wider offerings to more than 1500 clients across the globe. Their offerings include:

eCommerce Development: Professional eCommerce solutions to grow business online.

Magento Development: We have developed sophisticated Magento extensions that can seamlessly connect and synchronize with your eCommerce stores. Our Magento developers and Magento theme/template designers can customize Magento to match your business needs.

Mobile Application Development: Extensive expertise and experience in custom mobile application software development and Mobile Applications using latest techniques.

Content Management Systems: We offer comprehensive enterprise content management services so that organizations can enjoy complete control over the management of their websites and its related functionalities.

Web Development: Our web development team can develop anything from a basic website to complex web portals and web applications. Using well defined standards and frameworks our engineers deliver flexible, robust and secure solutions.

Web Designing: We have a highly expertise team of professionals who specialize in the areas that are mandate to design and produce world class results. If you’re looking for an animated flash banner or an animated product manual, we are able to do those things for you as well.

Interactive Marketing Services: Interactive marketing has benefits you will want to take advantage of and which i95Dev can help you with.

Staff Augmentation: We offer a full range of staff augmentation and talent acquisition services to deliver a workforce that is efficient and profitable.
